## 6. Migration Strategy

### 6.1 Initial Migration

```bash
# Generate migration from schema
pnpm prisma migrate dev --name init

# Apply to production
pnpm prisma migrate deploy
```

### 6.2 Post-Migration Raw SQL

After initial migration, apply raw SQL for:
1. Table partitioning
2. Partial indexes
3. Seed data

### 6.3 Rollback Strategy

1. Each migration has automatic rollback via Prisma
2. Manual rollback scripts for raw SQL changes
3. Database backups before any production migration

